  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lead and oversee daily construction site operations to ensure safety, quality, and schedule adherence. Coordinate resources and resolve on-site challenges to drive successful project execution and deliver measurable outcomes.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Monitor daily construction activities to enforce safety protocols and ensure compliance with building regulations</li><li>Coordinate subcontractors, personnel, and equipment to achieve project schedules and budget targets</li><li>Inspect ongoing and completed work to verify adherence to technical specifications and quality standards</li><li>Manage on-site materials by ensuring timely delivery and proper storage to prevent shortages and delays</li><li>Maintain detailed records of work progress and daily logs, providing accurate reports to project managers</li><li>Identify and resolve on-site issues, design challenges, or changes in project scope to maintain workflow continuity</li><li>Supervise and motivate on-site staff and subcontractors to optimize team performance and project outcomes</li><li>Utilize computer software to generate reports and manage project scheduling effectively</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in building or construction management, supporting effective site and project management</li></ul>",
